   <head>An admonition to <hi>the Reader.</hi>
   </head>
   <p>ALthough (beloued Reader) this Treatise, be not of those sort of Bookes, vvhich are vsually de<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>uided into Chapters, eyther short or long: yet, asvvell by notes in the mar<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>gent, as also by the tytles oboue the heade of euery leafe, you are no lesse plainlye directed to euery perticular matter therein, than by the other you might be.</p>
